    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Ah, apologies, I did have a look through the issues, but couldn't find anything that seemed to match.\r\n\r\nFor my use-case the doubling up of the transformation is the bigger issue. If it turns out it's necessary for the transformer to be called twice, would it be feasible for it to be passed the original, un-transformed hits array in both instances?",
