    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I see how that's problematic, for the time being I can only think of in transformItems *adding* new keys you plan to display instead of actually changing existing values.\r\n\r\nNot sure yet how, but I think we probably should avoid this as it could be considered a bug. I think it happens because we set the result of transformItems to `searchResults`, for mostly legacy reasons (not escaping multiple times)",
